convertUInt16ToFloat¶

zserio.float.convertUInt16ToFloat(float16Value)[source]¶

Converts 16-bit float stored as an integer value to python native float.

Parameters

float16Value – Half precision float value stored as an integer value to convert.

Returns

Converted python native float.
